      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in incredible shape\u2014it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one, kept it garaged, and it\u2019s spotless inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect and ready for a new home, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
