    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 represents a pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering, featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six equipped with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. The powertrain delivers a linear torque curve and a visceral 8,000 RPM redline, paired with a crisp 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis is structurally flawless, featuring documented subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec variable M differential lock for precise lateral transitions. Every suspension component, from the bushings to the dampers, retains original factory compliance, ensuring surgical steering response and optimal torsional rigidity. This is a turn-key, concours-level specimen with a comprehensive service history and zero mechanical compromises.",
